All Implemented Interfaces:
Serializable
public class Lshaped extends ObjectiveCard
Represents a specific type of objective card with additional corner and second color attributes, known as "Lshaped". This class extends ObjectiveCard to include additional attributes and functionalities specific to Lshaped cards.

      corner - an integer representing the corner associated with this objective
      secondColor - the CornerItem representing the second color for the objective
